<a href="#0" id="0">In this paper, we have presented a semi-automatic system for the automation of the keyword method and used it to teach 40 Italian words to 20 English native speakers.</a>
<a href="#1" id="1">We let the system select appropriate keywords and generate sentences automatically.</a>
<a href="#2" id="2">For each Italian word, we selected the most suitable among the 10 highest ranked suggestions and used it for the evaluation.</a>
